    Guide to honey production package

    Plotting Total Production Trend From 1998 to 2012

    production_plot.Rd

    A line graph showing total honey production trend by states in the US over time, which is a big picture of the honey production data.

    The output is the line graph of the honey production value for all states, regardless of whether argument has an input or not.

    Usage

    production_plot(allstates)

    Arguments

    allstates

    character. Every state of US from HoneyProduction dataset.

    Value

    A line graph containing the curve of the change in the total honey production of each state from 1998 to 2012.

    Examples

    production_plot()

    
production_plot(allstates = )
